HEADWORD: Scape-wheel
<hw>Scape"-wheel`</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <fld>(Horol.)</fld>
<def>The wheel in an escapement (as of a clock or a watch) into the
teeth of which the pallets play.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

